NOTICE

This model wrapper integrates Omni-DNA, a unified genomic foundation model
developed by Zehui Li, Vallijah Subasri, Yifei Shen, Dongsheng Li, Yiren Zhao,
Guy-Bart Stan, and Caihua Shan (Imperial College London, University of Toronto,
Microsoft Research, and collaborators).

Source: https://huggingface.co/zehui127/Omni-DNA-1B

